    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款具有挑战性的精准平台跳跃游戏中，奔跑、跳跃并逆转重力流向，以逃脱自私神祇的心灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演玛雅，某个被遗弃的孤独神祇一时兴起从家人身边偷走的孩子，在超过100个充满尖刺、激光、开关和陷阱的场景中前进，同时揭开你新监狱的恐怖秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010610/extras/5c9f03c8588c20b2a74775692b576da0.poster.avif?t=1771856126\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010610/extras/5c9f03c8588c20b2a74775692b576da0.webm?t=1771856126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010610/extras/5c9f03c8588c20b2a74775692b576da0.mp4?t=1771856126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >华丽的手绘像素美术风格，搭配包含数千帧精心打磨的逐帧动画，让神明的国度栩栩如生</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富且极具氛围感的配乐，优美动听却又令人不安</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >响应灵敏、干脆利落的操作手感，在带来挑战的同时，也赋予玩家极致的掌控感与施展杂技般的成就感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >心理恐怖叙事扭曲展开，揭示超越理解的选择</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010610/extras/8b3359049ee8d46cd2a913880b129e92.poster.avif?t=1771856126\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010610/extras/8b3359049ee8d46cd2a913880b129e92.webm?t=1771856126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010610/extras/8b3359049ee8d46cd2a913880b129e92.mp4?t=1771856126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能找到回家的路吗？还是会永远徘徊在这座由记忆雕刻而成的回廊之中？</p>",
